cursor.execut( ... )
cursor.fetchall( ... ) 

Convert tuple of tuples to row of rows for Pandas DF: [[i for i in r] for r in rows]


http://moderndata.plot.ly/graph-data-from-mysql-database-in-python/

Docker Image:
